<h3>Registration Form Fields</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Required</th><th>Maps To (Server)</th><th>Validation</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Full Name</td><td>text</td><td>Yes</td><td>fullName → users.name</td><td>Non-empty, max 100 chars</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Email Address</td><td>email</td><td>Yes</td><td>email</td><td>Valid email format, unique</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>tel</td><td>Yes</td><td>phone → users.phone, org_phone</td><td>Non-empty</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Business Name</td><td>text</td><td>Yes</td><td>org_name → organizations.name</td><td>Non-empty, max 200 chars</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Business Type</td><td>select</td><td>Yes</td><td>org_type → organizations.type</td><td>One of: retail, wholesale, franchise, distributor</td></tr>
  <tr><td>City / Address</td><td>text</td><td>No</td><td>org_address → organizations.address, branches.address</td><td>Max 500 chars</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Password</td><td>password</td><td>Yes</td><td>password (hashed)</td><td>Minimum 8 characters</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Confirm Password</td><td>password</td><td>Yes</td><td>–</td><td>Must match Password field</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Password Strength Indicator</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Score</th><th>Label</th><th>Color</th><th>Criteria Met</th></tr>
  <tr><td>1</td><td>Weak</td><td>Red</td><td>Only 1 of: length≥8, uppercase, digit, special char</td></tr>
  <tr><td>2</td><td>Fair</td><td>Amber</td><td>2 criteria</td></tr>
  <tr><td>3</td><td>Good</td><td>Teal</td><td>3 criteria</td></tr>
  <tr><td>4</td><td>Strong</td><td>Emerald</td><td>All 4 criteria</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Registration Workflow (Server Side)</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Validate inputs (name, email format, password length, org_name)</li>
  <li>Check email uniqueness in <code>users</code> table</li>
  <li>Generate unique org code from business name (e.g. "Ahmed Tyre" → "AHMED-TYRE")</li>
  <li>Insert into <code>organizations</code> table</li>
  <li>Insert first branch (<code>"Main Branch"</code>, code <code>"MAIN"</code>) into <code>branches</code></li>
  <li>Seed 12 default settings entries for the new organization</li>
  <li>Hash password with bcrypt (12 rounds), insert <code>org_admin</code> user with <code>branch_id = NULL</code></li>
  <li>Return <code>{ success: true, organization_id, branch_id }</code></li>
  <li>Frontend shows success banner for 1.8 seconds, then redirects to login</li>
</ol>

