<ul>
  <li><b>Left:</b> Hamburger menu (mobile only) + Dynamic page title + subtitle</li>
  <li><b>Right:</b> Notification bell (badge with count) → dropdown of alerts; User avatar → dropdown (org info, sign out)</li>
  <li><b>Notifications:</b> Overdue invoices (red severity), Pending purchase orders (warning severity) — clicking navigates to relevant page</li>
</ul>

<h3>News Banner</h3>
<p>A dismissable announcement bar displayed below the header. Content is controlled via <b>Settings → Company Profile → Announcement</b>. Hidden when announcement is empty.</p>

