<h2>8.2 PO Status Definitions</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Status</th><th>Color</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Stock Effect</th></tr>
  <tr><td>pending</td><td><span class="badge badge-amber">Amber</span></td><td>PO created, awaiting delivery</td><td>No stock change</td></tr>
  <tr><td>received</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Emerald</span></td><td>Goods received and stocked</td><td>+qty to each tire's stock</td></tr>
  <tr><td>cancelled</td><td><span class="badge badge-red">Red</span></td><td>PO cancelled (if previously received, stock reversed)</td><td>−qty if was received</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>8.3 New Purchase Modal — Form Fields</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Required</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Supplier</td><td>Searchable dropdown</td><td>Yes</td><td>Searches supplier name/code</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Date</td><td>date</td><td>Yes</td><td>Defaults to today</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Status</td><td>select</td><td>Yes</td><td>pending or received</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Notes</td><td>text</td><td>No</td><td>Appears on PO printout</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Line Items – Tire/Product</td><td>Searchable dropdown</td><td>Yes (min 1)</td><td>Searches tires + products</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Line Items – Qty</td><td>number</td><td>Yes</td><td>Min 1; if status=received, adds to stock</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Line Items – Unit Price</td><td>decimal</td><td>Yes</td><td>Purchase (cost) price</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>8.4 Purchase Business Rules</h2>
<ul>
  <li>PO number auto-generated: <code>[POPrefix]-[YEAR]-[NNN]</code> (e.g. PO-2024-001)</li>
  <li>When status changes to <b>received</b>: each tire line item's stock is incremented</li>
  <li>When status changes to <b>cancelled</b> from received: stock is decremented (floor at 0)</li>
  <li>Deleting a received PO also decrements stock</li>
  <li>Purchase payments update <code>purchases.amount_paid</code> and insert into <code>ledger_entries</code></li>
</ul>

