<h2>10.2 Add/Edit Tire Form Fields</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Required</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Brand</td><td>text</td><td>Yes</td><td>e.g. Bridgestone, Michelin, General</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Model</td><td>text</td><td>Yes</td><td>e.g. B-250, Energy Saver</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Size</td><td>text</td><td>Yes</td><td>e.g. P195/65R15, 205/55R16</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Tire Type</td><td>select (from lookup)</td><td>Yes</td><td>Populated from tire_types lookup table</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Stock (Qty)</td><td>integer ≥ 0</td><td>Yes</td><td>Current stock level</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Reorder Level</td><td>integer ≥ 0</td><td>No</td><td>Triggers Low Stock alert when stock ≤ this</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Cost Price</td><td>decimal ≥ 0</td><td>No</td><td>Purchase cost per unit</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Sale Price</td><td>decimal ≥ 0</td><td>Yes</td><td>Selling price per unit</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Notes</td><td>text</td><td>No</td><td>Internal notes about this SKU</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>10.3 Inventory Business Rules</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Stock is <b>decremented</b> when a sale is created with tire line items</li>
  <li>Stock is <b>incremented</b> when a purchase is received (status=received)</li>
  <li>Stock floor is 0 (never goes negative via system operations)</li>
  <li>Margin % = ((Sale Price − Cost Price) / Cost Price) × 100</li>
  <li>Low Stock = stock ≤ reorder_level (defaults: if reorder_level is 0 or null, no alert)</li>
  <li>Stock Value = SUM(stock × cost_price) for all tires in branch</li>
</ul>

<h2>10.4 Excel Import Format (Inventory)</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Column</th><th>Required</th><th>Format</th></tr>
  <tr><td>brand</td><td>Yes</td><td>Text</td></tr>
  <tr><td>model</td><td>Yes</td><td>Text</td></tr>
  <tr><td>size</td><td>Yes</td><td>Text e.g. P195/65R15</td></tr>
  <tr><td>tire_type</td><td>No</td><td>Exact name from tire_types lookup</td></tr>
  <tr><td>stock</td><td>Yes</td><td>Integer ≥ 0</td></tr>
  <tr><td>reorder_level</td><td>No</td><td>Integer</td></tr>
  <tr><td>cost_price</td><td>No</td><td>Decimal</td></tr>
  <tr><td>sale_price</td><td>Yes</td><td>Decimal</td></tr>
</table>

