│ [A] Ahmed Hassan      │  📞 +92-300-xxx  ✉ ahmed@mail           │
│ CUST-001              │  📍 Lahore                               │
│ PKR 6,000 owed ──→    │                                          │
│ [████████░░] 80%      │  Balance: PKR 6,000          [💳 Pay]   │
│                       │                                          │
│ [B] Bilal Khan        │  Invoiced: 12,000 | Paid: 6,000 | Due:6,000│
│ CUST-002              │                                          │
