│                       │  │Date  │Type    │Ref    │Dr  │Cr│Bal │  │
│                       │  │Jan15 │Invoice │INV-001│12K │  │12K │  │
│                       │  │Jan20 │Payment │RCP-001│    │6K│6K  │  │
│                       │  └───────────────────────────────────┘  │
└───────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────┘</div>

<h2>13.2 Statement Entry Types</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Entry Type</th><th>Tab</th><th>Debit Column</th><th>Credit Column</th><th>Balance Effect</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Invoice</td><td>Receivables</td><td>Invoice total</td><td>–</td><td>Balance increases (customer owes more)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Payment</td><td>Receivables</td><td>–</td><td>Payment amount</td><td>Balance decreases (customer paid)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Purchase</td><td>Payables</td><td>–</td><td>PO total</td><td>Balance increases (we owe supplier)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Payment</td><td>Payables</td><td>Payment amount</td><td>–</td><td>Balance decreases (we paid supplier)</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>13.3 Running Balance Logic</h2>
<ul>
  <li><b>Receivables:</b> running_balance = previous_balance + debit − credit</li>
  <li><b>Payables:</b> running_balance = previous_balance + credit − debit</li>
  <li>Entries ordered by entry_date ASC, then created_at ASC</li>
  <li>Statements are <b>org-wide</b> (show all branches) to present complete account history</li>
</ul>

<h2>13.4 Record Payment Modal (LedgerPaymentModal)</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Amount</td><td>decimal</td><td>Required; must be &gt; 0</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Payment Date</td><td>date</td><td>Defaults to today</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Payment Method</td><td>select</td><td>Cash, Bank Transfer, Cheque, Card</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Reference No</td><td>text</td><td>Optional: cheque/transfer number</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Apply To</td><td>list of unpaid invoices/POs</td><td>Multi-select with individual amounts</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Notes</td><td>text</td><td>Optional</td></tr>
</table>

