<h1>Appendix A: Color Code Reference</h1>
<table>
  <tr><th>Color</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Used For</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Teal (#0d6e6e)</td><td>Primary brand / positive action</td><td>Buttons, active nav, paid status, receivables</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Emerald</td><td>Success / positive financial</td><td>Paid status, collected amounts, settled badge</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Amber/Yellow</td><td>Warning / pending</td><td>Pending status, low stock, partial payment</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Red</td><td>Error / overdue / critical</td><td>Overdue status, negative balance, low stock alert</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Blue</td><td>Info / in-progress</td><td>Partial status, invoice entries, revenue metrics</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Violet/Purple</td><td>Payables / suppliers</td><td>Supplier avatars, payables tab, purchase-related</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Slate/Grey</td><td>Neutral / secondary</td><td>Table headers, disabled states, secondary text</td></tr>
</table>

<h1>Appendix B: Keyboard &amp; UX Patterns</h1>
<table>
  <tr><th>Pattern</th><th>Behavior</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Search fields</td><td>Real-time filter (onChange); no submit needed</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Modal close</td><td>X button top-right; also closes on backdrop click (most modals)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Status badges</td><td>Clickable dropdown in Sales table for quick status change</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Hover actions</td><td>Edit/Delete buttons appear on hover in Customer/Supplier/Inventory cards</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Toast notifications</td><td>Auto-dismiss after 2.5 seconds; top-right fixed position</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Sidebar collapse</td><td>Desktop: 256px expanded / 72px icon-only collapsed; tooltips on hover when collapsed</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Responsive breakpoints</td><td>mobile &lt; 1024px (bottom nav), tablet 1024–1280px (collapsed sidebar), desktop &gt; 1280px</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Empty states</td><td>All list/table views show descriptive empty state message when no data</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Loading states</td><td>Spinner shown while API calls in progress; buttons disabled during save</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Error states</td><td>Inline field errors (registration), alert box at top of modal (operations), global error page (load failures)</td></tr>
</table>

